<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>WIN BOT — Analista WINM26</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #050a0e;
    --panel: #090f14;
    --border: #0d2030;
    --accent: #00c896;
    --red: #ff3a5c;
    --yellow: #f5c518;
    --blue: #00aaff;
    --text: #cde8f5;
    --muted: #4a6a80;
    --glow: 0 0 18px #00c89655;
    --glow-red: 0 0 18px #ff3a5c55;
  }
  * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  body { background:var(--bg); color:var(--text); font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; min-height:100vh; overflow-x:hidden; }
  body::before {
    content:''; position:fixed; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:9999;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(0,200,150,.013) 2px,rgba(0,200,150,.013) 4px);
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:14px 24px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#050a0e 60%,#081520);
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:200;
  }
  .logo { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:1.25rem; color:var(--accent); letter-spacing:3px; text-shadow:var(--glow); }
  .logo em { color:var(--text); opacity:.5; font-style:normal; }
  .hdr-right { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; }
  .live-badge { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.72rem; color:var(--accent); }
  .dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--accent); animation:pulse 1.3s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;box-shadow:0 0 0 0 #00c89688} 60%{opacity:.5;box-shadow:0 0 0 6px transparent} }
  #clock { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.82rem; color:var(--muted); }
  #auto-label { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.65rem; color:var(--muted); }
  #auto-label.on { color:var(--accent); }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .main { max-width:940px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px 16px 80px; }

  /* ── PRICE BAR ── */
  .price-bar { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:10px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .pc {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px;
    padding:13px 15px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .pc::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background:var(--accent); }
  .pc.red::before { background:var(--red); }
  .pc.yellow::before { background:var(--yellow); }
  .pc.blue::before { background:var(--blue); }
  .pc-lbl { font-size:.6rem; color:var(--muted); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; }
  .pc-val { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:1.35rem; font-weight:700; margin-top:3px; color:var(--accent); }
  .pc.red .pc-val { color:var(--red); }
  .pc.yellow .pc-val { color:var(--yellow); }
  .pc.blue .pc-val { color:var(--blue); }

  /* ── MINI CHART ── */
  .chart-wrap {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px;
    padding:14px 18px; margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .chart-header { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .chart-title { font-size:.62rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2.5px; color:var(--muted); }
  .chart-legend { display:flex; gap:14px; font-size:.62rem; color:var(--muted); font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
  .chart-legend span { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; }
  .chart-legend i { width:10px; height:2px; display:inline-block; }
  canvas#priceChart { width:100% !important; height:120px !important; display:block; }

  /* ── SIGNAL BOX ── */
  .signal-box {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:16px; overflow:hidden;
    transition:border-color .3s;
  }
  .signal-box.sell { border-color:#ff3a5c44; }
  .signal-box.buy  { border-color:#00c89644; }
  .signal-header {
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:13px 20px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); background:#060d12;
  }
  .sig-title { font-size:.65rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:3px; color:var(--muted); }
  .sig-badge {
    font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.73rem;
    padding:3px 12px; border-radius:3px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1px;
  }
  .b-sell { background:#ff3a5c22; color:var(--red);    border:1px solid var(--red); }
  .b-buy  { background:#00c89622; color:var(--accent); border:1px solid var(--accent); }
  .b-wait { background:#f5c51822; color:var(--yellow); border:1px solid var(--yellow); }
  .signal-body { padding:18px 20px; }
  .entry-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .eg { text-align:center; }
  .eg-lbl { font-size:.58rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:3px; }
  .eg-val { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:700; }
  .c-en { color:var(--yellow); }
  .c-st { color:var(--red); }
  .c-t1 { color:var(--accent); }
  .c-t2 { color:#7fffcf; }
  .rr-row { font-size:.73rem; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:13px; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; align-items:center; }
  .rr-row strong { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; color:var(--accent); }
  .analyst-text {
    font-size:.8rem; line-height:1.75; color:#8ab8cc;
    border-left:3px solid var(--accent); padding-left:13px; font-style:italic;
  }
  .signal-box.sell .analyst-text { border-left-color:var(--red); }

  /* ── SECTION TITLE ── */
  .sec { font-size:.62rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:3px; color:var(--muted); margin:22px 0 11px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }
  .sec::after { content:''; flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--border); }

  /* ── SENTIMENT ── */
  .sent-lbl { font-size:.62rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:5px; }
  .sent-bar { height:9px; border-radius:5px; background:#0d2030; overflow:hidden; display:flex; margin-bottom:5px; }
  .s-bull { background:var(--accent); transition:width 1.2s; }
  .s-bear { background:var(--red);    transition:width 1.2s; }
  .sent-meta { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:.63rem; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
  .sent-meta .m-bull { color:var(--accent); }
  .sent-meta .m-bear { color:var(--red); }

  /* ── INDICATORS ── */
  .ind-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:9px; }
  .ind {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px;
    padding:11px 13px;
  }
  .ind-name { font-size:.58rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--muted); }
  .ind-val  { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.9rem; margin-top:3px; }
  .ind-sig  { font-size:.62rem; margin-top:2px; }
  .bull { color:var(--accent); }
  .bear { color:var(--red); }
  .neut { color:var(--yellow); }

  /* ── SIGNAL HISTORY ── */
  .hist-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:7px; }
  .hist-item {
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:70px 70px 1fr 80px 70px;
    align-items:center; gap:10px;
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:7px;
    padding:10px 14px; font-size:.75rem;
  }
  .hist-item.win  { border-left:3px solid var(--accent); }
  .hist-item.loss { border-left:3px solid var(--red); }
  .hist-item.open { border-left:3px solid var(--yellow); }
  .h-time { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; color:var(--muted); font-size:.68rem; }
  .h-dir  { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-weight:700; }
  .h-dir.sell { color:var(--red); }
  .h-dir.buy  { color:var(--accent); }
  .h-pts { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
  .h-pts.pos { color:var(--accent); }
  .h-pts.neg { color:var(--red); }
  .h-pts.open { color:var(--yellow); }
  .h-status { font-size:.6rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; padding:2px 7px; border-radius:3px; text-align:center; }
  .h-status.win  { background:#00c89618; color:var(--accent); }
  .h-status.loss { background:#ff3a5c18; color:var(--red); }
  .h-status.open { background:#f5c51818; color:var(--yellow); }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .tl { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0; }
  .tl-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:88px 20px 1fr; gap:0 10px; align-items:start; }
  .tl-time { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.72rem; color:var(--yellow); text-align:right; padding-top:5px; }
  .tl-spine { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; }
  .tl-dot { width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; border:2px solid var(--accent); background:var(--bg); margin-top:5px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .tl-line { flex:1; width:1px; background:var(--border); min-height:28px; }
  .tl-card {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:7px;
    padding:9px 13px; margin-bottom:8px;
  }
  .tl-ev  { font-size:.78rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:2px; }
  .tl-dsc { font-size:.72rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.5; }

  /* ── FUNDAMENTAL ── */
  .fund-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; }
  .fund-card { background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; padding:13px 15px; }
  .fund-title { font-size:.62rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .fi { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:.75rem; margin-bottom:5px; color:#8ab8cc; }
  .fi span:last-child { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
  .fi.pos span:last-child { color:var(--accent); }
  .fi.neg span:last-child { color:var(--red); }
  .fi.neu span:last-child { color:var(--yellow); }

  /* ── NEWS ── */
  .news-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
  .ni {
    background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-left:3px solid var(--border); border-radius:7px;
    padding:11px 15px; cursor:pointer; transition:border-color .2s,background .2s;
  }
  .ni:hover { background:#0c1820; }
  .ni.bull { border-left-color:var(--accent); }
  .ni.bear { border-left-color:var(--red); }
  .ni.neut { border-left-color:var(--yellow); }
  .ni-meta { display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .ntag {
    font-size:.58rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px;
    padding:2px 7px; border-radius:3px; background:#0d2030; color:var(--muted);
  }
  .ntag.bull { background:#00c89618; color:var(--accent); }
  .ntag.bear { background:#ff3a5c18; color:var(--red); }
  .ntime { font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:.62rem; color:var(--muted); margin-left:auto; }
  .nh { font-size:.8rem; font-weight:700; line-height:1.4; }
  .nb { font-size:.73rem; color:var(--muted); margin-top:5px; line-height:1.55; display:none; }
  .ni.open .nb { display:block; }

  /* ── BUTTONS ── */
  .btn-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; margin-top:22px; }
  .btn {
    padding:13px; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;
    font-size:.75rem; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; border:1px solid;
    transition:all .2s; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00c89611,#00c89622);
    border-color:var(--accent); color:var(--accent);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background:#00c89633; box-shadow:var(--glow); }
  .btn-secondary {
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#0af1,#0af2);
    border-color:var(--blue); color:var(--blue);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background:#0af3; box-shadow:0 0 18px #0af5; }
  .btn:disabled { opacity:.4; cursor:not-allowed; }
  .spin { display:none; }
  .loading .spin { display:inline-block; animation:spin .7s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes spin { to{transform:rotate(360deg)} }

  /* ── NOTIFICATIONS ── */
  #notif-area { position:fixed; bottom:20px; right:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; z-index:1000; pointer-events:none; }
  .notif {
    background:#090f14; border:1px solid var(--accent); border-left:4px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius:8px; padding:11px 15px; font-size:.76rem; max-width:310px;
    box-shadow:var(--glow); animation:slideIn .3s ease, fadeOut .4s ease 4.6s forwards;
    pointer-events:all;
  }
  .notif.sell { border-color:var(--red); border-left-color:var(--red); box-shadow:var(--glow-red); }
  .notif.wait { border-color:var(--yellow); border-left-color:var(--yellow); }
  .notif-title { font-weight:700; font-size:.8rem; margin-bottom:2px; }
  @keyframes slideIn { from{transform:translateX(40px);opacity:0} to{transform:translateX(0);opacity:1} }
  @keyframes fadeOut { from{opacity:1} to{opacity:0} }

  /* ── PROGRESS BAR (auto-refresh) ── */
  #progress-bar {
    position:fixed; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px;
    background:var(--border); z-index:500;
  }
  #progress-fill { height:100%; background:var(--accent); width:0%; transition:width .5s linear; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media(max-width:600px){
    .price-bar { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .entry-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .ind-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .fund-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .hist-item { grid-template-columns:55px 55px 1fr 60px; }
    .hist-item .h-status { display:none; }
    header { flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
    .btn-row { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">WIN<em>/</em>BOT <em style="font-size:.65rem;opacity:.35">v3.0</em></div>
  <div class="hdr-right">
    <div id="auto-label">AUTO: OFF</div>
    <div class="live-badge"><div class="dot"></div> AO VIVO</div>
    <div id="clock">--:--:--</div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="main">

  <!-- PRICE BAR -->
  <div class="price-bar">
    <div class="pc">
      <div class="pc-lbl">WINM26</div>
      <div class="pc-val" id="last-price">177.685</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pc red">
      <div class="pc-lbl">Variação</div>
      <div class="pc-val" id="variation">-0,34%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pc yellow">
      <div class="pc-lbl">Range do Dia</div>
      <div class="pc-val" id="day-range">1.735 pts</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pc blue">
      <div class="pc-lbl">Tendência</div>
      <div class="pc-val" id="trend-lbl">LATERAL</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MINI CHART -->
  <div class="chart-wrap">
    <div class="chart-header">
      <div class="chart-title">📈 Preço — Últimas 20 Barras (30min)</div>
      <div class="chart-legend">
        <span><i style="background:var(--accent)"></i> Preço</span>
        <span><i style="background:var(--yellow)"></i> MM20</span>
        <span><i style="background:var(--red); opacity:.6"></i> Resistência</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <canvas id="priceChart"></canvas>
  </div>

  <!-- SIGNAL -->
  <div class="signal-box sell" id="main-signal">
    <div class="signal-header">
      <div class="sig-title">⚡ Sinal do Analista IA</div>
      <div class="sig-badge b-sell" id="sig-badge">▼ VENDA</div>
    </div>
    <div class="signal-body">
      <div class="entry-grid">
        <div class="eg"><div class="eg-lbl">Entrada</div><div class="eg-val c-en" id="sig-entry">178.200</div></div>
        <div class="eg"><div class="eg-lbl">Stop</div><div class="eg-val c-st" id="sig-stop">178.900</div></div>
        <div class="eg"><div class="eg-lbl">Alvo 1</div><div class="eg-val c-t1" id="sig-t1">177.000</div></div>
        <div class="eg"><div class="eg-lbl">Alvo 2</div><div class="eg-val c-t2" id="sig-t2">176.200</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rr-row">
        R/R: <strong id="sig-rr">1 : 2,4</strong>
        &nbsp;|&nbsp; Parcial 50% no Alvo 1
        &nbsp;|&nbsp; Mover stop para zero ao atingir Alvo 1
      </div>
      <div class="analyst-text" id="analyst-comment">
        Fechamento abaixo da abertura com topos descendentes confirma pressão vendedora. Mercado rejeitou a região de 178.800 duas vezes no 30min. Aguardar pullback para a zona de entrada com candle de confirmação antes de executar.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SENTIMENTO -->
  <div class="sec">Sentimento do Mercado</div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:16px">
    <div class="sent-lbl">Fluxo Comprador vs Vendedor</div>
    <div class="sent-bar"><div class="s-bull" id="bull-bar" style="width:38%"></div><div class="s-bear" id="bear-bar" style="width:62%"></div></div>
    <div class="sent-meta"><span class="m-bull" id="bull-pct">↑ 38% Comprado</span><span class="m-bear" id="bear-pct">62% Vendido ↓</span></div>
  </div>

  <!-- INDICADORES -->
  <div class="sec">Indicadores Técnicos (30min)</div>
  <div class="ind-grid" style="margin-bottom:16px">
    <div class="ind"><div class="ind-name">RSI (14)</div><div class="ind-val bear" id="rsi-val">44,2</div><div class="ind-sig bear">Zona de fraqueza</div></div>
    <div class="ind"><div class="ind-name">MACD</div><div class="ind-val bear">Cruzamento ↓</div><div class="ind-sig bear">Sinal de venda</div></div>
    <div class="ind"><div class="ind-name">Média 20</div><div class="ind-val neut">178.120</div><div class="ind-sig bear">Preço abaixo da MM</div></div>
    <div class="ind"><div class="ind-name">Média 200</div><div class="ind-val bull">175.840</div><div class="ind-sig bull">Suporte estrutural</div></div>
    <div class="ind"><div class="ind-name">Bollinger</div><div class="ind-val neut">Banda média</div><div class="ind-sig neut">Lateralização</div></div>
    <div class="ind"><div class="ind-name">Volume</div><div class="ind-val bear" id="vol-val">Abaixo da média</div><div class="ind-sig neut">Sem confirmação</div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- HISTÓRICO DE SINAIS -->
  <div class="sec">Histórico de Sinais de Hoje</div>
  <div class="hist-list" id="hist-list">
    <div class="hist-item win">
      <div class="h-time">09:32</div>
      <div class="h-dir sell">▼ VENDA</div>
      <div style="font-size:.73rem;color:var(--muted)">Entrada 178.650 → Alvo 1 atingido</div>
      <div class="h-pts pos">+850 pts</div>
      <div class="h-status win">✓ Gain</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hist-item loss">
      <div class="h-time">11:15</div>
      <div class="h-dir buy">▲ COMPRA</div>
      <div style="font-size:.73rem;color:var(--muted)">Entrada 177.300 → Stop acionado</div>
      <div class="h-pts neg">-400 pts</div>
      <div class="h-status loss">✗ Loss</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hist-item win">
      <div class="h-time">14:05</div>
      <div class="h-dir sell">▼ VENDA</div>
      <div style="font-size:.73rem;color:var(--muted)">Entrada 178.200 → Alvo 2 atingido</div>
      <div class="h-pts pos">+1.550 pts</div>
      <div class="h-status win">✓ Gain</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hist-item open">
      <div class="h-time" id="open-time">--:--</div>
      <div class="h-dir sell" id="open-dir">▼ VENDA</div>
      <div style="font-size:.73rem;color:var(--muted)">Sinal atual — em aberto</div>
      <div class="h-pts open">Em curso</div>
      <div class="h-status open">● Aberto</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TIMELINE -->
  <div class="sec">Mapa de Horários — Hoje</div>
  <div class="tl">
    <div class="tl-row">
      <div class="tl-time">09:00–09:30</div>
      <div class="tl-spine"><div class="tl-dot" style="border-color:var(--yellow)"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div>
      <div class="tl-card"><div class="tl-ev" style="color:var(--yellow)">⚠️ Abertura — Alta Volatilidade</div><div class="tl-dsc">Evitar operar nos primeiros 15min. Aguardar definição de direção. Observar se rompe ou rejeita o preço de abertura.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-row">
      <div class="tl-time">09:30–11:00</div>
      <div class="tl-spine"><div class="tl-dot" style="border-color:var(--accent)"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div>
      <div class="tl-card"><div class="tl-ev" style="color:var(--accent)">✅ Janela Prime — Melhores Setups</div><div class="tl-dsc">Maior liquidez e tendência definida. Executar sinal com confirmação no candle de 30min. Melhor janela para day trade.</div></div>
    </div>
